CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1953, page 22, reads: "Samples- Attractive Miss Mozella Hairston passed samples of Braun's Town Talk Bread, to the many who visited this unusual exhibit which was set up Edward Wallace, assistant sales manager of the Braun Baking Company (not shown)."
TitMainTitle: Mozella Hairston standing in Braun Baking Company booth advertising Town Talk Bread, 1953 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, Ammon Center
